flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Scheduled DRP planning run or new DRP/STR signal from Kinaxis/S4 indicating allocation changes, inventory imbalances, or demand/constraint shifts.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest master and transactional inputs (forecasts, inventory, allocations, transport/costs)]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast + Safety Stock Service - Compute updated demand, safety stock and allocation impact]
  N2 --> N3{Agent: Agentic AI (orchestrated via Process Builder / Agent Team) - Agentic AI evaluates trade-offs and proposes per-SKU/location DRP Adjustment vs STR Release}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder - Remote Functions - Execute approved changes: write DRP adjustments to Kinaxis and STR releases to S4; record plan impacts]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle + UI Screen - Open CWB Lifecycle items for exceptions and surface execution results to planners]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder Notification + Subject Areas - Notify stakeholders and persist outcomes to Subject Areas for downstream reporting]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Closed-loop DRP cycle with automated execution of optimal distribution decisions, measurable reductions in COGS and holding costs, improved working capital, maintained or improved service levels, faster plan execution, and tracked exceptions with auditable approval/override history.]
  N3 -->|Agentic AI recommends STR Release for...| B1[Agentic AI falls back to DRP Adjustment with rebalancing and flags a CWB for expedited approval if business requires]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Avoids excessive transport cost while surfacing exception for potential executive override]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Multiple conflicting recommendations ...| B2[Create a multi-party Agent Team subprocess to run scenario negotiation, present top N tradeoff options, and open CWB Lifecycle for selected scenario]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Transparent, negotiated resolution that balances multi-echelon constraints with auditable rationale]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Human reviewer rejects agent recommen...| B3[Process Builder records the override, triggers Remote Function to revert scheduled writebacks if already executed, and logs rationale for model retraining]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Safe rollback, audit trail for continuous learning, and retraining signal for Agentic AI/Cortex]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]